Global Sweeping Robot Market Insights
Sweeping Robot Market size was valued at USD 5.20 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.45 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.26% from 2024 to 2030.

Sweeping Robot Market Overview
The sweeping robot market is projected to grow significantly, with an estimated market value reaching approximately USD 15.34 billion by 2027, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 22.6% from 2020 to 2027. This growth is driven by increasing consumer demand for automated home appliances and growing technological advancements in robotics and AI. The rise in disposable incomes and the growing trend of smart homes are key factors contributing to market expansion. Additionally, the COVID-19 pandemic has accelerated the adoption of automated cleaning solutions, particularly in households and commercial spaces seeking efficient cleaning solutions.

